[[File:Cruise_missile_JSF.jpg|thumb|right|250px|One of [[Nym/Legends|Nym's]] cruise missiles in flight]]

A '''cruise missile''' was a high-powered missile propelled by a basic engine. The [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] had these weapons loaded into his [[Havoc (starfighter)|''Havoc'']] during the [[Occupation of Karthakk]], as did [[Reti]] and [[Jinkins]] on their craft, the ''[[Zoomer]]'' and ''[[Freefall]]'' respectively.

[[Trade Federation Cruiser (Second Battle of Lok)|Trade Federation cruisers]] also employed cruise missiles. Waves of these projectiles were launched at Nym's forces while assembling an [[Orbital Defense Cannon]] on [[Khons]].

